the belle 's stratagem is a romantic comedy of manners that received its premiere on 22 february 1780 and it was hannah cowley 's most successful work .   it drew its title from george farquhar 's play the beaux ' stratagem .   the show was presented by david garrick , filling the 2,000-seat drury lane theatre and it became a major hit of the season .   queen charlotte enjoyed the play so much that she decreed it be performed for the royal family once a season for several years .